<section class="roadmap-section" id="roadmap" aria-labelledby="roadmap-heading">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="reveal">
      <p class="section-label">Vem por aí</p>
      <h2 id="roadmap-heading" class="section-title section-title--center">Roadmap público — evolução contínua.</h2>
      <p class="section-desc section-desc--center">Transparência do que estamos priorizando. Sem promessa de data pública; ajustamos conforme feedback de quem usa.</p>
    </div>
    <ul class="roadmap-list">
      <li class="roadmap-item reveal">
        <span class="roadmap-pill">Planejado</span>
        <span class="roadmap-text">{{ lavacash.ios.badge }} — {{ lavacash.ios.roadmap }}{% if lavacash.ios.waitlistUrl %} <a href="{{ lavacash.ios.waitlistUrl }}">Lista de espera</a>{% endif %}</span>
      </li>
      <li class="roadmap-item reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <span class="roadmap-pill">Em estudo</span>
        <span class="roadmap-text">Melhorias nos relatórios e exportação</span>
      </li>
      <li class="roadmap-item reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <span class="roadmap-pill">Contínuo</span>
        <span class="roadmap-text">Ajustes de UX com base no uso real</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
